{"tid":1578912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［十一行動］支那大國慶，我要見到旗杆上嘅係香港人嘅旗！","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T23:10:43.000Z","uid":40121,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f7df90f2cd212f656b4f729a22e64aec4adadd23","tid":1578912,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"抽氣扇同支那大旗都代表唔到香港人<br />\n十月一號，共匪支旗係金紫荊升起，港旗就要係對面海升起！<br />\n<br />\n我要升港旗有無人跟機！<br />\n多過十個人留tg就一齊搞！<br />\n利申無特殊技能只有心<br />\n<br />\n至於升咩旗可以睇下呢度<br />\n香港之旗，由你決定！【香港旗設計大賽】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f4bdae02af287666a36f71f4a239dcb4fa94ba7","tid":1578912,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:40:28.000Z","msg":"想像一下全民黑衣"},{"pid":"27e213c9d51dc894f959e41badc990f3baf7dccc","tid":1578912,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:40:39.000Z","msg":"對住旗桿肅立"},{"pid":"45fe955e484403b622935facc689e1e6856e719d","tid":1578912,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"旗慢慢升起"},{"pid":"7a85714ad2999fe9433fbe717998b3c4f360d0c1","tid":1578912,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"係《榮光》之中抵達旗桿頂"},{"pid":"7fea5b556ca6aa9d3d00ea20085286f20296a80c","tid":1578912,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"有咩比呢個晝面更振奮人心！"},{"pid":"ddfbd59e95778721f676034b17b500d318592f69","tid":1578912,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我嘗試過去google search &ldquo;Chinazi&rdquo;、&rdquo;Revolution of Our Times&rdquo; 發現根本<span style=\"color: red;\">冇一個網址有詳細介紹</span>，即是話一直以黎我地個概念只係得同溫層知，外國人連懶人包都冇</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人地連你搞咩都未清楚，點stand w